Tang-Yau (arXiv:2602.04140):
  Symbol matrix M_m(t): encodes constraint matrices for all eigenspaces
  C_m^(k) = M_m(omega^k): evaluation at k-th root of unity
  Stability: rank(M_m(t)) constant for generic t


